visitRelationalExpression

public void visitRelationalExpression(com.code.aon.ql.ast.RelationalExpression expression)
This method is called by a RelationalExpression. Print 2 expressions separated by its operator:
< if ((expression.type & RelationalExpression.LT) > 0)
> if ((expression.type & RelationalExpression.GT) > 0)
= if ((expression.type & RelationalExpression.EQ) > 0)
<> if ((expression.type & RelationalExpression.NEQ) > 0)
LIKE if ((expression.type & RelationalExpression.LIKE) > 0)
